726104f-a.title: Queens: Atlantic Avenue - Lefferts Boulevard
726104f-a.text:
Atlantio Avenue,east from and across Lefferts Boulevard,
showing the Morris Park station of the Long Island Railroad,
and a signal tower.
P. L. Sperr  May 7, 1934
